# Terrateam
[Infrastructure Orchestration for Terraform, OpenTofu, CDKTF, and Terragrunt](https://terrateam.io)

## What happens after installation?
You'll be redirected to the [Terrateam docs](https://terrateam.io/docs) for setup instructions.

## Will I be charged? No
You get a 14-day free trial with full access to all features. After the trial, you'll be automatically downgraded to our free plan unless you choose to provide payment details to continue with premium features. 

## GitHub permissions and Security
See our [Security](https://terrateam.io/security) page to learn more.

---
By installing, you agree to the [Terms of Service](https://terrateam.io/terms) and [Privacy Policy](https://terrateam.io/privacy).
